divs: sighting details07\25\09 12:55 am sitka alaska. while outside with my wife looking at the constellations i notice one star like object moving at a casual rate very high above the planet its appeared to be swaying slightly back and forth. i turn and say look ufo to my wife then point. she sees it. we stare for about 2 min before it goes beyond the trees line, so there we both have out first ufo sighting. after thoughts- im am no sceptic could have been a spy plane but no. we saw it so defeats that. satalite? no. it was not exactly on a straight path. no to baloons. shuttle no..comet or meteo..no. i read universetoday.com they usualy mention shooting stars and stuff. top secret government project could be it i admit but why can we see it so no.
